      <StorageSelectors>&lt;StorageSelector&gt;&lt;Selector&gt;&lt;Process Name="1cv8c" /&gt;&lt;UIElement Name="ЗУП 3 / Зарплата и управление персоналом КОРП, редакция 3.1" ClassName="V8TopLevelFrameSDI" ControlType="Window" /&gt;&lt;UIElement ControlType="Pane" /&gt;&lt;UIElement Index="17" ControlType="Pane" /&gt;&lt;UIElement ControlType="Pane" /&gt;&lt;UIElement ControlType="Pane" /&gt;&lt;UIElement ControlType="Pane" /&gt;&lt;UIElement Index="4" ControlType="Pane" /&gt;&lt;UIElement ControlType="Pane" /&gt;&lt;UIElement ControlType="Pane" /&gt;&lt;UIElement ControlType="Pane" /&gt;&lt;UIElement ControlType="Pane" /&gt;&lt;UIElement ControlType="Pane" /&gt;&lt;UIElement Index="1" ControlType="Pane" /&gt;&lt;UIElement ControlType="Pane" /&gt;&lt;UIElement Index="28" ControlType="Pane" /&gt;&lt;UIElement Name="Дата рождения:" ControlType="Edit" /&gt;&lt;/Selector&gt;&lt;ThumbImageID&gt;757ac54a-1d26-4668-a69f-3cbb972edf41&lt;/ThumbImageID&gt;&lt;Snapshot /&gt;&lt;Created&gt;13.02.2026 14:02:38&lt;/Created&gt;&lt;/StorageSelector&gt;&lt;StorageSelector&gt;&lt;Selector&gt;&lt;Process Name="1cv8c" /&gt;&lt;UIElement Name="ЗУП 3 / Зарплата и управление персоналом КОРП, редакция 3.1" ClassName="V8TopLevelFrameSDI" ControlType="Window" /&gt;&lt;UIElement ControlType="Pane" /&gt;&lt;UIElement Index="17" ControlType="Pane" /&gt;&lt;UIElement ControlType="Pane" /&gt;&lt;UIElement ControlType="Pane" /&gt;&lt;UIElement ControlType="Pane" /&gt;&lt;UIElement Index="4" ControlType="Pane" /&gt;&lt;UIElement ControlType="Pane" /&gt;&lt;UIElement ControlType="Pane" /&gt;&lt;UIElement ControlType="Pane" /&gt;&lt;UIElement ControlType="Pane" /&gt;&lt;UIElement ControlType="Pane" /&gt;&lt;UIElement Index="1" ControlType="Pane" /&gt;&lt;UIElement ControlType="Pane" /&gt;&lt;UIElement Index="27" ControlType="Pane" /&gt;&lt;UIElement Name="Дата рождения:" ControlType="Edit" /&gt;&lt;/Selector&gt;&lt;ThumbImageID&gt;06a7a2a7-1803-49e3-a8e9-ca1de4f81303&lt;/ThumbImageID&gt;&lt;Snapshot /